{"tid":2259950,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"利物浦即將趁國際賽期遷移大本營 - 11月中啟用斥資5000萬鎊興建的訓練中心","createTime":"2020-10-27T08:11:37.000Z","updateTime":"2020-11-03T05:40:47.000Z","uid":67225,"like":3,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":19,"replies":[{"pid":"cd05d87bcba2befa9640ac0b4638b230d3b1970a","tid":2259950,"uid":67225,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-27T08:11:37.000Z","msg":"利物浦將會在11月中的國際賽期時將一隊的訓練從Melwood搬到Kirkby，正式告別Melwood訓練中心，令球隊的青訓和一隊能在同一個地方訓練，以便高普去觀察其他梯隊的發展。<br />\n<br />\n斥資5000萬鎊去進行的Kirkby訓練中心改建工程佔地約24公頃，比原本5公頃的Melwood訓練中心大好幾倍，內裡包括7個草地球場及3個混合草場，還有兩個守門員訓練區、兩個室內人造草場、小型網球場、泳池、健身室等設備。<br />\n<br />\n高普在2017年和FSG共同推動這個將一隊訓練和青訓集於一身的Kirkby訓練基地，在2018年動工的時候，高普表示這裡可以成為利市的足球總部，令年青梯隊和一隊的距離能夠縮短。<br />\n<br />\n原本曾傳出球隊會在今季都繼續使用Melwood，但現在最新消息是高普希望推動在11月的時候遷移到Kirkby，球會將會在短期內正式公佈消息，而且據報會同時公佈有關訓練中心命名權的事宜。"},{"pid":"c8394b599818a80f3d64255de83344ecdd5c83b9","tid":2259950,"uid":67225,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-27T08:12:27.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://www.thisisanfield.com/wp-content/uploads/liverpool-training-ground-kirkby-.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thisisanfield.com%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2Fliverpool-training-ground-kirkby-.jpg&h=a7b6c1b0&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"f21a03bcbfd0c82aa7b5c124b8b4b3e6937fee6d","tid":2259950,"uid":44285,"like":26,"dislike":0,"score":26,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2020-10-27T08:53:23.000Z","msg":"有錢起training ground無錢出糧要staff乞食<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\nYou'll Never Walk Again<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0e72ce02d534f3f847498f404dfd99770276ee35","tid":2259950,"uid":8968,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"f21a03bcbfd0c82aa7b5c124b8b4b3e6937fee6d","tid":2259950,"uid":44285,"like":26,"dislike":0,"score":26,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2020-10-27T08:53:23.000Z","msg":"有錢起training ground無錢出糧要staff乞食<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\nYou'll 